quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,Iqeôb ed yimir; ifelleq waggur
  54,2,"Ma walan assekni, ad wexxôen, ad inin: \"ipkemmil ssêur"
  54,3,"Nekôen, îîafaôen lemcihwat nnsen. Ad iûaô yal lameô"
  54,4,"Ni$ usan ten id kra isallen, u wayen degsen iswexxiôen"
  54,5,Üûwab issakwayen. Maca ula iwumi aâaggen
  54,6,"Ihi, îîixxeô asen! Asmi ara d isiwel, uberraê, ar wayen iwaâôen"
  54,7,"s wallen ibran, ara d ff$en si tneîlin, am ujôad iwezzâen"
  54,8,"Ad éedmen, âaooôen, ar uberraê, ad inin ijehliyen: \"wagi d ass uwâiô"
  54,9,"Agdud n Nuê, uqbel nnsen, iskaddeb. Skaddben amdan nne$. Nnan: \"d aôehbani\". Rran t id"
  54,10,"Inuj ar Mass is: \"nek pwa$elbe$, Awes"
  54,11,"Nelli tibbura igenni, i waman d ihedman"
  54,12,"Nesgguffaâ d laânaûeô n tmurt, mlalen waman akken ipwagzem lameô"
  54,13,"Nebbwi t af tencirin, akked tavuî n tiffest"
  54,14,"Teppeddu zdat wallen nne£, d arraz i win ipwanekôen"
  54,15,Ni$ Neooa p id d assekni. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,16,Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,17,Ni$ Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,18,Âad skaddben. Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,19,"Ih, Nuzen asen aûeôûaô, ass amekêus, imezgi"
  54,20,Ippawi medden amzun d iqeôôumen n tezdayin ipwaqelâen
  54,21,Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,22,Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,23,Tamud skaddben aâeggen
  54,24,"Nnan: \"day a neddu d yiwen n umdan segne$? Ihi, nekwni, war ccekk, di ttelfan, akked tisselbi"
  54,25,"Day d neppa, garane$, u$uô id iusa uneddeô? Wanag neppa, d akeddab uqbiê"
  54,26,"Ad walin azekka, anwa ay d akeddab uqbiê"
  54,27,"A Nazen, ih, tal$wemt i ujeôôeb nnsen. Qaôaâ ten, ili k d aûebôi"
  54,28,Xebbeô iten ar aman ad pwafeôqen. Mkul tissit s tidwelt
  54,29,"Ssawlen i umeddakwel nnsen. Iusa d, igezm as ivaôen"
  54,30,Amek illa uqeîîi W u llant licaôat iW
  54,31,"Nuzen asen d, s tidep, yiwen usu$u. U$alen am alim di tbergent"
  54,32,Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,33,Agdud n Luî skaddben aâeggen
  54,34,"Ihi, Nuzen asen ajebwani, kkes ed tawacult n Luî, i Nsellek qbel tafara"
  54,35,d l$it s$uône£. Akka ay Nepkafi wid isnemmiren
  54,36,"Ni$ iâaggen asen, Newâaô. Rran aâeggen di ccekk"
  54,37,"Ni$ ssutren t $ef inebgawen is. Nesder$el allen nnsen: \"jeôôbet aâaqeb iW, akked uâaggen iW"
  54,38,"Iusa ten id, ssbeê zik, uâaqeb imezgi"
  54,39,"Jeôôbet aâaqeb iW, akked uâeggen iW"
  54,40,Nsehhel Leqwôan i usmekti. Day llan wid id ismektayen
  54,41,Ni$ iusa n uâeggen ar twacult n Ferâun
  54,42,"Skaddben issekniyen nne£, meôôa. Naâtad iten s ufus ioehden, izemren"
  54,43,Aâni ijehliyen nnwen ifen wigi? Ne$ tesâam laânaya deg Ihellilen
  54,44,"Ne$ a d inin: \"nekwni d agraw ara irebêen"
  54,45,"Agraw ad ixseô, ad wexxôen"
  54,46,"Ih, imir d ppaâud nnsen. Imir d lhejna, u ôéag kteô"
  54,47,"Ih, ibe$wdiyen di ttelfan akked tisselbi"
  54,48,"Asmi ara kkerkren ar tmes, $ef udmawen nnsen: \"jeôôbet tanalit ujajiê"
  54,49,"Ih, yal cci, Nxelq it s lmizan"
  54,50,"Lameô nne£ siwa yiwen, am unqej n tiî"
  54,51,Ni$ Nesqucc wid i kwen icban. Day llan wid ara d ismektin
  54,52,Yal igi nnsen deg Ihellilen
  54,53,"Akw, meééi meqqweô, ppujerrden"
  54,54,"Wid ipêezziben, s tidep, di leonanat akked isaffen"
  54,55,"deg umekkan n tidep, ar Ugellid Uzmir"